Usko tha samjhana ki yeh nayi zindagi meri.
Raaton ko mai sota na, paap nashe mein dhota na.
Fir karta usse dobara, 2:12 baje raat ke jab uthi woh bagal se,
Aake kaanon mein kaha ki mera jeene ka na mann hai.
Tu hai nahi woh jisne mere saath khaayi kasmein, kya poori karni rasmein, ab adhoore mere sapne.

Ha mai jaanti bura hua hai bohot tab bane tum yeh,
Par kaato ke bin baagho ke gulab bhi na mehkenge.
Hum seh lenge akelapan jo ayega, par yeh safar yehi tak reh jayega.
Da da dum, da da dum....

verse:
sub seey pahale aakhir kyaa thaa? main bataata huun
sub seey pahale God they aur unake saath ack sharabi bhee thaa
God apane creation mein mast rahate aur sharabi apane recreation mein
jaba jaba sharabi kii daaroo khatm hoe jaati, voe God seey kahata, "Ayy God, meraa bottley khatam hoe gaela haye"
aur God kahate, "abey yaar, yeye leey tuu, khush reh, kaam karane dey"
aur sharabi kii bottle apane aap phir seey bhar jaati
dheere dheere sharabi kii peene kii speed badhane luggy aur voe God seey drinks paye drinks banavaane lagaa
phir ack baar sharabi key liye dinn kaa chauttiswan drink banaate hue, God koo saste theke key bartender vaali feel aaee
aur taba God ney socha, "aise naheen chalega, iss bevade kaa kuchh karna hii padegaa, maybe sudharne kaa kuchh motivation diyaa jaae"
taba God ney ack jadui bottle banaai aur buggle mein ack behad komal, sunder aur meethi khushbu vaale laal rung key foolon kaa ack adbhut paudha lagaaya, aur sharabi koo voe bottle dey dee
phir God ney sharabi seey kahaa, "jaba bhee teree yeye bottle khaali hogi, iss paudhe seey ack fool jhada key sookh jaayega aur teree yeye bottle apane aap bhar jaayegi. mugger yeye paudha mast flourish karey, yeye assure karane key liye tujhe ise rose ack bottle paani chadhaana hoga"
"yeye tou mast haye God, ispe daaroo hii chadhaa duun kyaa? yeye bhee mast bhand hoe jaayega"
"kadaapi naheen, bitch, unnerth hoe jaayega"
"Alright, alright"
phir sharabi ney shuruat kii apani best life kii: constant nashe key hazy blur mein jeene lagaa
tunn hoe jaane kii usaki chull itani zyaadaa thee kii usey dou second bhee rukna manzoor naheen thaa, usey zindagi bhar, lagaatar peena thaa
lagaatar peene kii iss chull key chakkar mein usane dimag daudaaya aur usey ack jordar idea aaya
uthaai apani bottle aur paudhe key buggle mein hii shift hoe gayaa, abb tou buss rukna thaa hii naheen
rose kissy tarah tunn haalat mein voe paudhe koo ack bottle paani chadhaata, phir peene kii naee hadein paar kartaa
usaki zindagi abb harr rose buss isi sawal kaa jawab dene mein nikalati kii "aaj main kitni botalen chadhaa sakata huun?"
aur usane khoob chadhaai, lagaatar chadhaai, aur harr bottle koo aakhari buund taka peeya, that is, until the day he didn't
haan, ack raat kuchh alag huaa, shayed sharabi laparwah hoe gayaa thaa, yaa shayed abb usey sharaab kii kadar naa thee, yaa shayed voe buss thakaa huaa thaa
joe bhee thaa, usa raat, usaki chull usase aage nickle gaee aur voe haath mein aadhi bharee bottle key saath pass out hoe gayaa, paudhe key buggle mein
And soon enough, unnerth hoe gayaa
Passed out sharabi key haath seey voe aadhi bharee sharaab kii bottle dhul gaee aur paudhe kii jadon taka sharaab pahunch gaee

inhin paudhon mein seey ack God kii gaand key thheek neeche ugane lagaa, phir God koo gaand key neeche halki khujali hui

verse:
curry bahut mistakes (Mistakes)
parr chhode naheen dost (chhode naheen dost)
yahaan paye they saanp (saanp)
Right under my nose (Nose)
jalaa dee gend (jalaa dee gend)

abb baney voe hater (baney voe hater)

poochhe, "kyaa haye cost?" (poochhe, "kyaa haye cost?")
maine kahaa mehnat haye baave yeye paise seey hatake, a lot (A lot)
Twenty one floors (Twenty one floors)
jaise final boss (Final boss)
haye luggy baahar bheed (bheed)
jaise ander haye Shah Rukh Khan
curry mistakes parr chhode naheen loga

Ah fuck it, main jaane naheen detaa huun dushman koo jaise main jaane naheen detaa huun dost koo
pahala, main fuck detaa huun apane music koo
doosara, main fuck detaa huun apane moksh koo

bahan paye baat haye aaa jaati tou khou detaa huun apane hosh koo, I mean (Aha)
mujhe kiss baat kii sherm haye, main chala rhaa huun karmon paye
ack baat boll, tujhe kiss baat kaa bhram haye?

humm cull seey hain behtar aur aaj bhee hain dheet

ainth (Ungh), londe rahey hain mujhase ainth (Aha)

baalak rahey hamse ainth (ainth)
baap koo dikhaate naheen ainth (ainth)

meraa harr track hater'on kii halak mein duss jagah seey futt rhaa haye
